    <string name="locationPermissionScreen_explanation">The My Driving Style app requires access to your vehicle\'s GPS data to accurately analyse your driving behaviour and to provide key features such as challenges, driver analytics and other gamification elements. This data is essential for ensuring the app functions as intended. Without location permission, these features cannot be enabled and the app will not be usable.\n\nTo proceed, please grant permission by following the path:\n\nOpen settings &gt; Permissions &gt; Location &gt; Allow all the time</string>
    <string name="notificationPermissionScreen_explanation">The My Driving Style app requires access to notifications in order to keep you informed about important updates, relevant changes and exclusive offers. Enabling notifications ensures that the My Driving Style app works as intended and that you don’t miss out on key information related to your driving analytics and app features. Without this permission, you may not receive essential alerts.\n\nTo proceed, please grant permission by following the path:\n\nGrant permission &gt; Allow</string>
    <string name="notificationPermissionScreen_explanation2">The My Driving Style app requires access to notifications in order to keep you informed about important updates, relevant changes and exclusive offers. Enabling notifications ensures that the My Driving Style app works as intended and that you don’t miss out on key information related to your driving analytics and app features. Without this permission, you may not receive essential alerts.\n\nTo proceed, please grant permission by following the path:\n\nOpen settings &gt; Activate notification toggle</string>
